OL,6,FLike many across the UK, she was later
OL,7,Ftold that she was given contaminated
OL,8,Fblood which meant she has been living
OL,9,Fwith hepatitis C ever since.
OL,11,FShe says they are still no further
OL,12,Fforward with compensation for victims
OL,13,Fof the blood contamination scandal
OL,14,Fthan they were a year ago when the
OL,15,Freport was revealed.
OL,17,FShe said: "The money is only important
OL,18,Fbecause it's symbolic that they did
OL,19,Fsomething wrong and now they're trying
OL,20,Fto fix it.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
