OL,3,CDelays to infected blood compensation
OL,4,Care 'a betrayal', victim says
OL,6,F"The hardest part of this process is
OL,7,Fwatching friends struggling with
OL,8,Fhealth problems. It is a betrayal.
OL,10,F"We'd taken it at face-value, that the
OL,11,FTories who had just left, had taken
OL,12,Finto account the seriousness of the
OL,13,Freport, they all said how appalling it
OL,14,Fwas, how compensation was long-overdue
OL,15,Fand how they were working at pace.
OL,17,F"Then we find out that nothing had
OL,18,Fbeen put into place at all."
