OL,6,FThe report accused both government and
OL,7,Fhealth officials of "deception",
OL,8,Fincluding destroying documents to
OL,9,F"save face and save expense".
OL,11,FA year on from that report, victims
OL,12,Fand their families are still waiting
OL,13,Ffor compensation to be handed out.
OL,15,FShe said: "I consider myself one of
OL,16,Fthe lucky ones, I'm still standing and
OL,17,Frelatively healthy.
