OL,6,F"But within our friendship network
OL,7,Fmany are critically ill, we've lost
OL,8,Fmore over the past year and the toll
OL,9,Fon our mental health is bad. A lot of
OL,10,Fus are exhausted."
OL,12,FIn the UK, blood donations were
OL,13,Faccepted from high-risk groups such as
OL,14,Fprisoners until 1986.
