OL,4,Care 'a betrayal', victim says
OL,6,FNick Thomas-Symonds, the government
OL,7,Fminister responsible for overseeing
OL,8,Fthe compensation rollout, told ITV
OL,9,FNews he hoped people would be paid as
OL,10,Fquickly as possible, and that the
OL,11,Fsystem he inherited after the General
OL,12,FElection was not working efficiently.
OL,14,FHe added that he was trying to speed
OL,15,Fup the process, but did not want to do
OL,16,Fanything that might delay payments
OL,17,Ffurther. He said he accepted that some
OL,18,Fpeople will die while waiting for
OL,19,Fcompensation.
