OL,6,FJoan added: "We focus on the money
OL,7,Fbecause it's the only vehicle of
OL,8,Fredress we have, we are in it because
OL,9,Fwe never want this to ever happen
OL,10,Fagain.
OL,12,F"We need mechanisms to never let this
OL,13,Fhappen to the public again. To have
OL,14,Fsome legislation in place where people
OL,15,Fcan be prosecuted if they have lied,
OL,16,Fis the only way we can go.
